SEC. 2. Section twenty-six of the same Act, as amended, is further amended to read as follows:

"SEC. 26.

Compensation of City Fiscal and his assistants.

â

"The City Fiscal and his assistants shall receive the salaries hereinafter set forth, which shall be paid by Pasay City:

"(a) The city fiscal, an annual compensation which shall be equal to that allowed or may hereafter be allowed for Judges of the Court of First Instance;

"(b) First assistant city fiscal, at eighteen thousand pesos

per annum;

"(c) Second assistant city fiscal, at seventeen thousand four hundred pesos

per annum;

"(d) Three third assistant city fiscals, at sixteen thousand eight hundred pesos

per annum;

each;

"(e) Four fourth assistant city fiscals, at sixteen thousand two hundred pesos

per annum;

each;

"(f) Five fifth assistant city fiscals, at fifteen thousand six hundred pesos

per annum;

each;

"(g) Five sixth assistant city fiscals, at fifteen thousand pesos

per annum;

each."

SEC. 3. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.

Approved, August 4, 1969.
